'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2558] on 3 September 2000 at 3:44:21 pm'!"Change Set:		023-BrowserAlphabet-SqRDate:			3 September 2000Author:		Andres Valloud	  This alphabetizer puts the categories starting with 'private' at theend. The private message categories are also alphabetized on their own."!!Browser methodsFor: 'message category functions' stamp: 'SqR 7/11/2000 20:36'!alphabetizeMessageCategories	| categories privateCategories publicCategories newCategories |	classListIndex = 0 ifTrue: [^ false].	self okToChange ifFalse: [^ false].	Smalltalk changes reorganizeClass: self selectedClassOrMetaClass.	categories _ self rawMessageCategoryList.	privateCategories _ categories select:		[:theOnes | (theOnes findString: 'private' startingAt: 1 caseSensitive: false) = 1].	publicCategories _ categories copyWithoutAll: privateCategories.	newCategories _ publicCategories asSortedCollection asOrderedCollection		addAll: privateCategories asSortedCollection;		yourself.	self classOrMetaClassOrganizer categories: newCategories asArray.	self clearUserEditFlag.	self editClass.	self classListIndex: classListIndex.	^ true! !!Browser reorganize!('accessing' contents contents:notifying: contentsSelection couldBrowseAnyClass doItReceiver editSelection noteSelectionIndex:for: request:initialAnswer: spawn:)('class functions' buildClassBrowser buildClassBrowserEditString: classListMenu: copyClass defineClass:notifying: editClass editComment explainSpecial: fetchClassDocPane fileOutClass findMethod hierarchy makeNewSubclass plusButtonHit printOutClass removeClass renameClass)('class list' classList classListIndex classListIndex: classListSingleton recent selectClass: selectedClass selectedClassName toggleClassListIndex:)('code pane' compileMessage:notifying: showBytecodes)('copying' veryDeepInner:)('drag and drop' acceptDroppingMorph:event:inMorph: acceptMethod:dstMessageCategory:srcMessageCategory:dstClass:dstClassOrMeta:srcCla